Motion2D 1.3.7 is an open source release.


This file describes the changes between Motion2D 1.3.6 and 1.3.7.

****************************************************************************
*                           General                                        *
****************************************************************************

- Add new motion models, support new image file format.

****************************************************************************
*                           Library                                        *
****************************************************************************

- In CMotion2DModel, addition of new motion models: 
   . MDL_TY,
   . MDL_AFF_TX_NULL, 
   . MDL_AFF_TY_NULL, 
   . MDL_AFF_DIV_NULL, 
   . MDL_AFF_ROT_NULL,
   . MDL_AFF_HYP1_NULL, 
   . MDL_AFF_HYP2_NULL. 
  To know more about these motion models see CMotion2DModel::EIdModel.
- In CMotion2DEstimator, addition of a new method estimate() able to proceed
  with an unsigned char support.
- CMotion2DImage supports the following image file formats: PNG and PNM. The
  different PNM formats are: PGM (P5), PPM (P6).

****************************************************************************
*                           Examples                                        *
****************************************************************************

- The Motion2D example:
   . support now the new motion models,
   . addition of some options (-a and -c) to specify the estimation support
     to consider. This option precise a video sequence path where each image 
     will be considered as support.
   . addition of some options (-j, -k, -t, -v) to fix the size of the 
     back-warped image sequence and the position of the first proceeded 
     frame in this sequence.
   . support for PNG and PNM (PPM P6) image file format.

- The Warping example: 
   . support for PNG and PNM (PPM P6) image file format.

